{"sha": "73e412b6d47f38560903b5faba0805fe208d7731", "node_id": "C_kwDOAAsO6NoAKDczZTQxMmI2ZDQ3ZjM4NTYwOTAzYjVmYWJhMDgwNWZlMjA4ZDc3MzE", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2023-04-04T04:48:35Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2023-04-04T04:48:35Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #10592 - beetrees:parent-dir-bug-fix, r=giraffate\n\nFix bug with getting parent directories in `lookup_conf_file`\n\nCurrently `lookup_conf_file` doesn't canonicalize the configuration directory before using [`PathBuf::pop`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/std/path/struct.PathBuf.html#method.pop) to get the parent directory. This isn't usually an issue when clippy is invoked via `cargo clippy` as `CARGO_MANIFEST_DIR` is already canonicalized. However, this currently causes `clippy-driver` to ignore any `clippy.toml` in any parent directories when  `CARGO_MANIFEST_DIR` and `CLIPPY_CONF_DIR` are not set.\n\nchangelog: Fix a bug that would cause parent directories not to be searched for `clippy.toml` when using `clippy-driver` directly.", "tree": {"sha": "0b45c81fb0691f7c6bf5fb4c3a9732619e2a90cb", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/0b45c81fb0691f7c6bf5fb4c3a9732619e2a90cb"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/73e412b6d47f38560903b5faba0805fe208d7731", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/73e412b6d47f38560903b5faba0805fe208d7731", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/73e412b6d47f38560903b5faba0805fe208d7731", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/73e412b6d47f38560903b5faba0805fe208d7731/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.githu